title: Cafe Inspiration
typeOfFood: Vegan, Raw, Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Estonian
description: Vegan restaurant with deli, plenty of raw food and gluten free bread and pizza. Cozy atmosphere with old-stone walls and access from the street. Expanded its menu in 2015 and offers daily soups and mains like a whole wheat pasta spinach-almond, a risotto with chantarelle mushroom, couscous, wraps and burgers. Also serves raw cakes and house-brewed beer.
